This app generates poster images from the first page of PowerPoint presentations, posters are created with the same filename as the original PowerPoint in a subfolder called ‘posters’.

Dependencies
Before running this app you need to install the latest versions of the following software:

ImageMagick
https://imagemagick.org/index.php

LibreOffice (needs to be installed in usual Program Files folder)
https://www.libreoffice.org/

Ghostscript
https://www.ghostscript.com/download/gsdnld.html
